WEBVTT

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:31.336
(Laughter)

00:00:31.360 --> 00:00:33.680
Milk is why mammals suck.

00:00:35.400 --> 00:00:37.296
At Arizona State University,

00:00:37.320 --> 00:00:39.256
in the Comparative Lactation Lab,

00:00:39.280 --> 00:00:42.056
I decode mothers' milk composition

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:45.056
to understand its complexity

00:00:45.080 --> 00:00:47.480
and how it influences infant development.

00:00:48.720 --> 00:00:51.080
The most important thing that I've learned

00:00:51.800 --> 00:00:56.920
is that we do not do enough
to support mothers and babies.

00:00:57.720 --> 00:00:59.896
And when we fail mothers and babies,

00:00:59.920 --> 00:01:03.280
we fail everyone
who loves mothers and babies: